# Build Documentation for XML-RPC Chat Application

## Project Properties

| Property | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `src.dir` | Source code directory (`src/`) |
| `bin.dir` | Compiled classes directory (`bin/`) |
| `lib.dir` | External libraries directory (`lib/`) |
| `jar.dir` | Output JAR files directory (`archive/`) |
| `doc.dir` | JavaDoc documentation directory (`doc/`) |

## Build Targets

### Main Targets

- `all`: Main target that executes `clean`, `compile`, and `jar-all`
- `clean`: Removes all generated directories (bin, archive, doc)
- `compile`: Compiles all source code
- `jar-all`: Creates JAR files for interfaces, client and server
- `doc`: Generates JavaDoc documentation

### Execution Targets

- `client`: Runs the chat client application
- `server`: Runs the chat server application

## Dependencies

Required libraries in `lib/` directory:
- `xmlrpc-2.0.jar`: XML-RPC implementation
- `commons-codec-1.16.0.jar`: Apache Commons Codec

## Build Commands

```bash
# Clean and rebuild everything
ant all

# Run the server
ant server

# Run the client
ant client

# Generate documentation
ant doc